Package: OGDrawR
Title: OGDraw-Style Circular Genome Maps for Plant Mitochondria
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zhicheng", "Jia", email = "zhicheng.jia@cau.edu.cn",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Parse GenBank files and draw OGDraw-style circular maps for plant
    mitochondrial genomes using the circlize package. Supports intron/exon
    visualization, GC content rings, and automatic label de-overlapping.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: circlize
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/zhichengjia/OGDrawR
BugReports: https://github.com/zhichengjia/OGDrawR/issues
